snippet.title: There Is No Game : Wrong Dimension (OFFICIAL TRAILER)
snippet.description:
Official trailer of the non-game called "There is no game : wrong dimension" from the indie studio Draw Me A Pixel.

Now Available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1240210

"There is no game: Wrong dimension" is a Point&Click comedy adventure (and Point&Click only!) that will take you on a journey you never asked to go on, through silly and unexpected video game universes.

Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/there-is-no-game-wrong-dimension-switch/
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.DMAP.Ting_WD&hl=fr&gl=US
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/there-is-no-game-wd/id1539133066
